{
  "spoken_lines": [
    {
      "key": "gq000_01_patch_intro_01",
      "string_id": "12775913875181139075",
      "speaker": "Patch",
      "addressee": "V",
      "text": "You made it. Good. Keep your voice down.",
      "audio_path": "mod\\gq000\\localization\\en-us\\vo\\patch_i_54a4cb510257868f.wem",
      "duration_ms": 3280
    },
    {
      "key": "gq000_01_v_choice_ghostline_line",
      "string_id": "1156091786248368624",
      "speaker": "V",
      "addressee": "Patch",
      "text": "Ghostline. Heard the name float around. Never saw the ghosts.",
      "audio_path": "mod\\gq000\\localization\\en-us\\vo\\v_i_c8b0de56507c08a5.wem",
      "duration_ms": 5200
    },
    {
      "key": "gq000_01_patch_rsp_ghostline_01",
      "string_id": "11078734689186137791",
      "speaker": "Patch",
      "addressee": "V",
      "text": "That's the point. We're not a gang, not a brand. We listen, collect, move things nobody wants traced.",
      "audio_path": "mod\\gq000\\localization\\en-us\\vo\\patch_i_239561f337d40388.wem",
      "duration_ms": 8560
    },
    {
      "key": "gq000_01_v_choice_whyyou_line",
      "string_id": "5242997719066938077",
      "speaker": "V",
      "addressee": "Patch",
      "text": "Plenty of mercs in Night City. Why pull me in?",
      "audio_path": "mod\\gq000\\localization\\en-us\\vo\\v_i_d2d2e820e86ddd3f.wem",
      "duration_ms": 3840
    },
    {
      "key": "gq000_01_patch_rsp_whyyou_01",
      "string_id": "374148180196916949",
      "speaker": "Patch",
      "addressee": "V",
      "text": "Because you get in, get out, and don't start asking the wrong questions before the eddies clear.",
      "audio_path": "mod\\gq000\\localization\\en-us\\vo\\patch_i_e099697a9adf8bde.wem",
      "duration_ms": 5920
    },
    {
      "key": "gq000_01_v_choice_job_line",
      "string_id": "13086211028292839137",
      "speaker": "V",
      "addressee": "Patch",
      "text": "Alright. Talk. What am I doing?",
      "audio_path": "mod\\gq000\\localization\\en-us\\vo\\v_i_44705c58f260bc8b.wem",
      "duration_ms": 5440
    },
    {
      "key": "gq000_01_patch_rsp_job_01",
      "string_id": "16644449196687460336",
      "speaker": "Patch",
      "addressee": "V",
      "text": "Tyger Claws are sitting on a relay that looks dead from the street. It isn't. Someone's laundering data through it.",
      "audio_path": "mod\\gq000\\localization\\en-us\\vo\\patch_i_2920c8e86a638bfa.wem",
      "duration_ms": 6960
    },
    {
      "key": "gq000_01_patch_rsp_job_02",
      "string_id": "9713432568750437441",
      "speaker": "Patch",
      "addressee": "V",
      "text": "You jack the node, pull the cache, and drop it where we tell you. Clean job, if nobody gets curious.",
      "audio_path": "mod\\gq000\\localization\\en-us\\vo\\patch_i_2920c7e86a638a47.wem",
      "duration_ms": 7040
    },
    {
      "key": "gq000_01_v_choice_client_line",
      "string_id": "67568872890781206",
      "speaker": "V",
      "addressee": "Patch",
      "text": "Tyger Claws don't move like that for free. Who's behind it?",
      "audio_path": "mod\\gq000\\localization\\en-us\\vo\\v_i_7eecd2c53138ef21.wem",
      "duration_ms": 4080
    },
    {
      "key": "gq000_01_patch_rsp_client_01",
      "string_id": "8240420351105930287",
      "speaker": "Patch",
      "addressee": "V",
      "text": "Someone Arasaka-adjacent. That's all you need. You want names, ask after the job's done.",
      "audio_path": "mod\\gq000\\localization\\en-us\\vo\\patch_i_115a20c9b938af44.wem",
      "duration_ms": 6320
    },
    {
      "key": "gq000_01_v_choice_accept_line",
      "string_id": "15809657832204668359",
      "speaker": "V",
      "addressee": "Patch",
      "text": "Fine. Send me the coordinates. I'll get your data.",
      "audio_path": "mod\\gq000\\localization\\en-us\\vo\\v_i_db51bdba3f0ece48.wem",
      "duration_ms": 3680
    },
    {
      "key": "gq000_01_patch_rsp_accept_01",
      "string_id": "1728179479238269697",
      "speaker": "Patch",
      "addressee": "V",
      "text": "Knew you would. Location's already queued.",
      "audio_path": "mod\\gq000\\localization\\en-us\\vo\\patch_i_25c9dffc088984c1.wem",
      "duration_ms": 3440
    },
    {
      "key": "gq000_01_patch_rsp_accept_02",
      "string_id": "10786705141388100709",
      "speaker": "Patch",
      "addressee": "V",
      "text": "Pull the cache, use the drop point, and don't improvise unless you have to.",
      "audio_path": "mod\\gq000\\localization\\en-us\\vo\\patch_i_25c9dcfc08897fa8.wem",
      "duration_ms": 4480
    }
  ],
  "choice_lines": [
    {
      "key": "gq000_01_v_choice_ghostline_short",
      "string_id": "914191732112522175",
      "text": "Ghostline?"
    },
    {
      "key": "gq000_01_v_choice_whyyou_short",
      "string_id": "3539648407476589212",
      "text": "Why me?"
    },
    {
      "key": "gq000_01_v_choice_job_short",
      "string_id": "3958656355326278376",
      "text": "What's the job?"
    },
    {
      "key": "gq000_01_v_choice_client_short",
      "string_id": "1612649723253519215",
      "text": "Who's behind it?"
    },
    {
      "key": "gq000_01_v_choice_accept_short",
      "string_id": "6832076283350341234",
      "text": "I'm in."
    }
  ],
